nitf
Class FieldWarning

java.lang.Object
  nitf.NITFObject
      nitf.DestructibleObject
          nitf.FieldWarning

public class FieldWarning
extends DestructibleObject

This class represents a Warning that is created by the NITF system while processing the data in some way. Usually a FieldWarning is created when a Field does not contain valid data.
